Package com.gsm.enums

Enum Permission

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Permission>
      • com.gsm.enums.Permission
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Permission>
    public enum Permission
extends java.lang.Enum<Permission>
    Defines all granular permissions in the system, grouped by functional module. This provides fine-grained control over user actions.
